
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-sarikaya-netlmm-lma-dnsdiscovery-03.txt'>
    <title>"Local Mobility Anchor Discovery Using DNS by Service Name", Behcet Sarikaya, Frank Xia</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-sarikaya-netlmm-lma-dnsdiscovery-03.txt</link>
    <description>This draft defines a Domain Name System (DNS)-based scheme to enable dynamic discovery of a Local Mobility Anchor (LMA) in Proxy Mobile IPv6.  DNS Service Resource Record option is used allowing a Mobile Access Gateway (MAG) to request the LMA's Fully Qualified Domain Name (FQDN) and possibly IPv6 address via the DNS response.  IPv4 case is also covered.</description>
    <dc:date>2010-05-03T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
